quotation: Do every act of your life as if it were your last.
speaker: Marcus Aurelius

quotation: Clouds come floating into my life, no longer to carry rain or usher storm, but to add color to my sunset sky.
speaker: Rabindranath Tagore

quotation: Everything in life that we really accept undergoes a change. So suffering must become Love. That is the mystery.
speaker: Katherine Mansfield

quotation: Life isn't about finding yourself. Life is about creating yourself
speaker: George Bernard Shaw

quotation: Attention to health is life greatest hindrance.
speaker: Plato

quotation: A man's life is what his thoughts make of it.
speaker: Marcus Aurelius

quotation: Choose your love, Love your choice.
speaker: Thomas S. Monson

quotation: We live in the world when we love it.
speaker: Rabindranath Tagore

quotation: A life spent making mistakes is not only more honorable, but more useful than a life spent doing nothing.
speaker: George Bernard Shaw

quotation: Our truest life is when we are in our dreams awake.
speaker: Henry David Thoreau

quotation: Accept responsibility for your life. Know that it is you who will get you where you want to go, no one else.
speaker: Les Brown

quotation: Every philosophy is the philosophy of some stage of life.
speaker: Friedrich Nietzsche
